list.abstract: 《inside》是丹麦独立游戏开发团队Playdead Studios制作并发行的一款冒险解密类游戏，于2016年6月29日上线Xbox One平台。 《inside》游戏为横版过关形式，整体属于末世启示录风格，十分阴暗诡异。画面进行了3D化，色彩更加艳丽。玩家需要操作一个小男孩，一边躲避各种敌人，一边进行解谜。 《inside》的最低配置需要Windows 7/8/10 （64-bit OS required）的操作系统，Intel Core 2的CPU，4GB的内存，GeForce 250 GTS的显卡，3GB的存储空间。推荐配置需要Windows 7/8/10 （64-bit OS required）的操作系统，Intel i7 920的CPU，8GB的内存，GeForce GTX 660的显卡，3GB的存储空间。曾获得北欧游戏大奖最佳音效奖、最佳美术奖等。
Inside是一首bang gang演唱的歌曲。

yingyinNormal.en: Drones! Get inside! Get inside!
yingyinNormal.zh: 是无人机！进去！快进去！

yingyinNormal.en: Those answers we carry inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些答案就在我们心中。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to have to go inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要下刀了。

yingyinNormal.en: Smackle, inside your head voice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 史麦科，你可以选择不说出来。

yingyinNormal.en: No way to get inside without a battle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要进去，势必得大战一场。

yingyinNormal.en: What! You can't keep me inside forever!
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么! 你不能永远关着我!

yingyinNormal.en: I told you, "look inside." In the note.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我告诉过你，纸条上有说往里面看。

yingyinNormal.en: Eep. Stay inside the family kill circle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小伊 待在家庭御战圈内。

yingyinNormal.en: If I take this away, you'll see the inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把这边拿开，你会看到里面。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's on the inside? There's got to be somebody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 到底谁是内鬼，肯定有这么个人。

yingyinNormal.en: He works so hard, he burns the energy from inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 金将军很认真工作，他练功发自内心。

yingyinNormal.en: You're wondering why you can't look inside my head.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你一定正奇怪为何无法探察我的脑海。

yingyinNormal.en: It is raining. Peppa and George have to stay inside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天下雨了，佩奇和乔治只能呆在家里。

yingyinNormal.en: The only person allowed inside this head is Dr. Phil.
yingyinNormal.zh: 唯一能检查[进入]我脑子的人是菲尔博士。

yingyinNormal.en: Zafar, I stashed something inside it. It's important.
yingyinNormal.zh: 扎法尔，我藏了一些东西在装置里，它很重要。

yingyinNormal.en: You're still just a little fat girl inside, aren't you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 内心深处的你仍是个小胖妹。

yingyinNormal.en: What's inside the locket, Maya, that's so important to you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛雅，吊坠里面到底是什么东西对你会那么重要？

yingyinNormal.en: These two Arabidopsis plants are being put inside a chamber.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这两株阿拉伯芥将被放进一个密闭的箱体。

yingyinNormal.en: Powder, hidden in plastic pouches inside their intestines. Excuse me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 粉末，装在塑料袋并藏在肠子里。你说什么？

yingyinNormal.en: So how are we gonna get inside? Wait. You want to get inside MLI?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们要怎么进去？等等，你们要进海博馆？

精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

examination_example.sentence: But I can give you several good reasons why people should remove their shoes before going <highlight>inside</highlight> their homes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是我可以给你几个很好的理由来解释为什么人们应该在进屋前脱鞋。

examination_example.sentence: For many in those countries, wiping their shoes before going <highlight>inside</highlight> is regarded as sufficient.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对那些国家的许多人来说，进去之前擦干净鞋子就足够了。

examination_example.sentence: A greater disaster was averted by members of the Paris fire brigade, who risked their lives to remain <highlight>inside</highlight> the burning monument.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 巴黎消防队成员冒着生命危险留在燃烧的纪念碑内，避免了一场更大的灾难。

examination_example.sentence: It was killing me <highlight>inside</highlight> because all that leather and fur went to waste and animals had died for nothing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我的内心非常痛苦，因为所有的皮革和毛皮都被浪费了，动物也白白死去了。

examination_example.sentence: With a book, the conversation takes place <highlight>inside</highlight> someone's head and without the risk of being judged by others.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有了书，对话就发生在某人的脑海里，没有被他人评判的风险。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Put the lunch <highlight>inside</highlight> the locker.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 把午餐放在柜子里。

examination_example.sentence: A bowl with a small hole floats (浮) in a water tank (水箱) <highlight>inside</highlight> the elephant's body.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个有小洞的碗漂浮在大象体内的水箱中。

examination_example.sentence: A few minutes later, he drove up  in a car, and put the suitcases <highlight>inside</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几分钟后，他开车过来，把手提箱放了进去。

examination_example.sentence: Now pull one thing out of the bag without looking <highlight>inside</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在从包里拿出一样东西，不要看里面。

examination_example.sentence: It looks cold but it’s warm <highlight>inside</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它看起来很冷，但里面很温暖。

examination_example.sentence: It was empty, but Jason could hear noises further <highlight>inside</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它是空的，但是杰生能听到更里面的噪音。

examination_example.sentence: It's <highlight>inside</highlight> and outside are decorated with giant panda pictures.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它的里里外外都装饰着大熊猫的图片。

examination_example.sentence: Bees can see colors we cannot, and they follow these to the <highlight>inside</highlight> of the flower.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 蜜蜂能看到我们看不到的颜色，它们跟着这些颜色来到花的内部。

examination_example.sentence: A wolf in sheep’s clothing describes someone who acts and looks nice on the outside but is bad on the <highlight>inside</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 披着羊皮的狼描述了一个外表看起来很好，但内心很坏的人。

examination_example.sentence: Many people like to sign their name on the <highlight>inside</highlight> cover.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多人喜欢在内封面上签名。
